message: Follow the hints carefully. 'Stove' a raw protein (beef/beans) first to get 20 value. Combine this with a grain (rice/corn/tortilla) for 40, then add a vegetable (carrot/tomato/mushroom/green beans) for 60. Do NOT use 'stove' again on the 60-value combined item; it will become 'overcooked' and drop to 45. Using 'water' on 'overcooked' items does not remove the 'overcooked' feature, only adds 'soaked' and usually retains the lower value. Be careful not to create 'overcomplicated' dishes, which have negative values.
